Class MessageClypeData

  • java.lang.Object
    • data.ClypeData
      • data.MessageClypeData
  • public class MessageClypeData
extends ClypeData
    Class that handles text messages that get transferred between CypeClients via the ClypeServer. Additionally handles the miscellaneous user input such as logging out and listing users
